                     <interp inst="t17340630-18-off86" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17340630-18-off86" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing a silk Turkey-quilt embroider'd, val. 5 l. and 3 Sattin Pillow-bears embroider'd, val. 20 s. the Goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17340630-18-victim202" type="victimName">
                           Daniel 
                           Layton 
                        <interp inst="t17340630-18-victim202" type="surname" value="Layton"></interp>
