                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17340630-18-defend200 t17340630-18-deflabel89"></join>) and a Man came down with a Bundle, like a silk Quilt, and said, You see, Mr. Ewer, I am as good as my Word, I'll lend you this to pledge; but let me have it again as soon as you can.</p>
